<lb ed="C I" n="0145a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>馬敬賢五十人等造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0145a01"/><p id="pI01p0145a0101">．．．族</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b01"/><p id="pI01p0145b0101">　□齊□保三年歲在壬申四月廿三日建。
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b02"/>　夫至理沖<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">凝</unclear>。絕<note n="0145001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30830;＝詮【史】</note><app n="0145001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">詮</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30830;</rdg></app><note n="0145002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30831;＝數【史】</note><app n="0145002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">數</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30831;</rdg></app>之表。法身<note n="0145003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30560;＝虛【史】</note><app n="0145003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30560;</rdg></app>洞。
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b03"/>　超有&CB07099;之境。是故如來。欲使迷駕迴
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b04"/>　<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">輪</unclear>。異路改轍。故託跡形名。以曉未悟。邑主
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b05"/>　馬敬賢合邑五十人等。各捨家珍。敬造石
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b06"/>　像一區。雕<note n="0145004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00496;＝飾【史】</note><app n="0145004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">飾</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00496;</rdg></app><note n="0145005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">庄＝莊【史】</note><app n="0145005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">莊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">庄</rdg></app>嚴。<note n="0145006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30329;＝鏤【史】</note><app n="0145006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鏤</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30329;</rdg></app>形精麗。伏願　皇帝。
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b07"/>　國祚永延。師僧父母。超越三界。託趣道場。
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b08"/>　彌勒出世。故能刊石鐫芳。用宣賢劫。
<lb ed="C I" n="0145b09"/>當陽像主馬雄</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0145c01"/><p id="pI01p0145c0101">．．．<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">連</unclear>　　清信．．．
<lb ed="C I" n="0145c02"/>．．．奴　　清信江要姬
<lb ed="C I" n="0145c03"/>．．．□　　清信□堂女
<lb ed="C I" n="0145c04"/>．．．養
<lb ed="C I" n="0145c05"/>．．．安生</p>
</div2>
